                	<h1 class="p2-7"><span style="color: #95b748;"><strong>Aloha and Welcome ~</strong></span></h1>
	
    <p class="p2-8">The choices you&rsquo;ve made in arriving here are not mistakes. &nbsp;Our greatest empowerment as spirit beings on this human journey is the decision and choice to heal ourselves. &nbsp;What are we healing? &nbsp;Well, I believe we are here to heal the ideas of separation, of being less than, too much, or not enough. &nbsp;Ultimately, we are here, healing the collective, to remember that we are all Divine in and of ourselves.<br /><br />Healing in this lifetime allows for healing across all dimensions of space and time - this life, past lives, and future lives. &nbsp;By placing importance upon ourselves and doing the work, as individuals we are having an impact on all of humanity by raising the vibration of ourselves, others, and the planet. &nbsp;By raising our vibration and shifting our energy, we not only heal ourselves, but we allow others to begin their healing process/journey as well by repairing the karmic links. This act of self-care and self-love is not only an empowerment for yourself, but it is an empowerment for the whole of LIFE.<br /><br />I am hoping you are here because you&rsquo;re being called to find greater meaning in your everyday life. &nbsp;I am hoping you are here because you&rsquo;re wanting to bring more joy into your Be-ing. I am hoping you are here because you are ready to begin to vibrate at a different frequency to attract more of what you love into your life, and through that increase in vibration, all the things that no longer serve you will surface to fall away.<br /><br />It is your choice, and I honor you for making it this far.<br /><br />Aho,<br />Andara</p>
